    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility is sufficient for a Medium model risk level. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted under risk-informed rationale: ASTM F1717 specifies a single standard configuration, model influence is Medium, and the three primary QoIs all satisfy the pre-established E/uval and percent-difference acceptance criteria across N=11 specimens at two independent laboratories. Package is submitted under ProfileMinimal; signature workflow is pending and will be applied prior to regulatory submission.",
